<div class="news-block content-panel">
<div class="panel-heading">
<p>News</p>
</div>
<div class="panel-body">
<div class="alternate unmargined">
<div class="news-title">
<p>October 7, 2018</p>
</div>
<div class="news-content">
<p>The international branches of the SCP community have teamed up to bring you a collection of translated SCPs from around the world! New articles are posted daily, and you can view them at the <strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-international">International Branches Hub</a></strong>!</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alternate unmargined">
<div class="news-title">
<p>August 17, 2018</p>
</div>
<div class="news-content">
<p>The <a href="/scp4000contesthub">SCP-4000 Contest</a> is over! Be sure to check out all the entries! <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-series-5">Series V</a> is now open!</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alternate unmargined">
<div class="news-title">
<p>July 12, 2018</p>
</div>
<div class="news-content">
<p><a href="/scpdeclassified">SCPDeclassified</a>, a <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/SCPDeclassified/">subreddit</a> devoted to literary analyses and plot explanations of SCP articles and concepts, recently reached 10,000 subscribers. Congratulations to them, and we look forward to reading their future declassifications!</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alternate unmargined">
<div class="news-title">
<p>June 20, 2018</p>
</div>
<div class="news-content">
<p>The <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp4000contesthub">4000 Contest</a> is live! In honor of the site's 10th anniversary, the contest's theme is HISTORY! Here's to an epic contest and another ten years of SCP!</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alternate unmargined">
<div class="news-title">
<p>May 21, 2018</p>
</div>
<div class="news-content">
<p>The <strong><a href="http://scp-pt-br.wikidot.com/">Portuguese Branch</a></strong> is the newest member of the International SCP community! We wish them the best of luck and great success!</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
